data.description: Discover the perfect blend of convenience and charm in Price Hill, just a quick 15-minute drive downtown and 25 minutes to CVG. Nestled in a prime location, this Victorian home boasts character and potential. With a few recent updates enhancing its appeal, the residence offers four bedrooms, one full and one-half bath, finished with beautiful stained glass and original woodwork. Enjoy the private deck and the convenience of off-street parking. Surrounded by parks, churches, and schools, adding to its appeal. New furnace and new water heater.
